Package commodities.util

Class Summary
CommodityCalendar The CommodityCalendar class extends the gregorian weekday calendar to override normal calendar functions for commodity processing.
DBTrilean The DBTrilean class is a three way switch similar to a boolean switch but has 3 positions.
Month The Month class is a table lookup of the variety of representations that are used for a given month in the commodities market.
PropertyManager The PropertyManager centrally manages property files.
